snippet.title: War Mongrels: Renegade Edition - Official PS5 Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
War Mongrels is an isometric real-time tactics game that takes place on the eastern front of World War II. War Mongrels is packed with dynamic and tactical gameplay with stealth elements, tightly packed into a dark, fascinating story. Players will be able to go in alone or in online co-op. War Mongrels is coming to PlayStation 5 and PlayStation 4 in Q1 2023.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
